OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. There will be a few
OL,8,Fshowers around, these may be briefly
OL,9,Fheavy across northern Aberdeenshire
OL,10,Fthis afternoon. Warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers dying out this
OL,13,Fevening. Then dry with clear spells,
OL,14,Fturning rather chilly in places.
OL,15,FThickening cloud will bring patchy
OL,16,Frain to the south later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
