OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,6,Frain for a time. Dry and somewhat
OL,7,Fbrighter in the afternoon. Further
OL,8,Frain spreading north in the evening.
OL,9,FWarm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry,
OL,12,Fbright and warm on Friday, chance of
OL,13,Fsome rain on Friday night. Then dry
OL,14,Fand warm over the weekend with some
OL,15,Fbrightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
